FR940406-1-00060 FR940406-1-00016 Therefore, it is proposed that 48 CFR parts 28 and 52 be amended as set forth below: 1. The authority citation for 48 CFR parts 28 and 52 continues to read as follows: Authority: 40 U.S.C. 486(c); 10 U.S.C. chapter 137; and 42 U.S.C. 2473(c). PART 28_BONDS AND INSURANCE 28.311&hyph;1 [Removed and redesignated] 2. Section 28.311&hyph;1 is removed. 28.311&hyph;2 [Redesignated and amended] 3. Section 28.311&hyph;2 is redesignated as section 28.311&hyph;1 and amended by removing the last two sentences. 28.311&hyph;3 [Redesignated] 4. Section 28.311&hyph;3 is redesignated as section 28.311&hyph;2. PART 52_SOLICITATION PROVISIONS AND CONTRACT CLAUSES 52.228&hyph;6 [Removed and reserved] 5. Section 52.228&hyph;6 is removed and reserved. 52.228&hyph;7 [Amended] 6. Section 52.228&hyph;7 is amended in the introductory paragraph by removing the citation ``28.311&hyph;2'' and inserting in its place ``28.311&hyph;1''; in paragraph (a)(1) of the clause by removing the words ``or in paragraph (h) of this clause (if the clause has a paragraph (h)),''; in paragraph (c) introductory text by removing the words ``Except as provided in paragraph (h) of this clause (if the clause has a paragraph (h)), the'' and inserting in its place the word ``The''; and by removing Alternates I and II at the end of the clause. 52.245&hyph;7 [Amended] 7. Section 52.245&hyph;7 is amended in the first sentence of paragraph (j) by removing the words ``in the clause at FAR 52.228&hyph;6, Insurance_Liability to Third Persons, or''. 52.245&hyph;10 [Amended] 8. Section 52.245&hyph;10 is amended in the first sentence of paragraph (f) by removing the words ``in the clause at FAR 52.228&hyph;6, Insurance_Liability to Third Persons or''. [FR Doc. 94&hyph;8145 Filed 4&hyph;5&hyph;94; 8:45 am] BILLING CODE 6820&hyph;34&hyph;M
